"><figure class="media-object-image img-header"><div class="image-container responsive-media"><img width="860" height="573" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-822240?width=860&amp;height=573" alt="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><figcaption class="imageCaption"><p class="imageCredit">照片：盖蒂图片社</p></figcaption></figure></div><p>关于您的社论“ <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/attorneys-general-letter-racial-preferences-hiring-fortune-100-companies-jonathan-skrmetti-kris-kobach-supreme-court-college-admissions-a2c5998e?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">对最高管理层的种族警告</a>”（7 月 14 日）：我第一次也是最后一次被要求做出基于非绩效的人事决定发生在大约 35 年前，当时我担任部门人事行动委员会的成员。在委员会向院长提交完全基于优点的候选人入围名单后，我们被告知该名单必须包括一名少数族裔候选人，即使他或她不是最合格的候选人之一。委员会拒绝了，我们辞职了。也许，几十年后，这种疯狂终于结束了。</p><p><strong>嗯。艾拉·索恩教授</strong></p><p><em>蒙特克莱尔州立大学</em></p><p><em>新泽西州上蒙特克莱尔</em></p></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 23 Jul 2023 16:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/affirmative-action-racial-preferences-faculty-hiring-diversity-90d3e391</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/affirmative-action-racial-preferences-faculty-hiring-diversity-90d3e391<category>教师招聘</category><category>平权行动</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论/意见</category><category>法激活过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 排除过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>IWE过滤器</category><category>信件</category><category>日常新闻</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>观点</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论</category><category>意见</category><category>法蒂瓦过滤器</category><category>c&amp;e 排除过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>伊威过滤器</category><category>字母</category><category>常规新闻</category><category>观点</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Wokeness Hobbles Disney as It Faces the Streaming Challenge]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div>无论如何，当收入下降时，用政治姿态疏远一半的观众无济于事。 <!-- data-module-name="article.app/lib/module/wsj/breadcrumbs" --><main id="main" role="main"><div class="wsj-article-headline-wrap crawler"></div><div class="articleLead" itemprop="articleLead" data-sbid="SB11277182998813654381604590099793198024332"></div><div class="articleBody" data-sbid="SB11277182998813654381604590099793198024332"><div class="clearfix bylineWrap"><div class="columnist_mini"> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/news/author/allysia-finley"><img width="45" height="45" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-772633/square" alt="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></a></div><div class="byline">作者： <span class="author" itemprop="name"><a href="https://www.wsj.com/news/author/allysia-finley" itemprop="url" rel="author">艾莉西亚·芬利</a></span></div><time class="timestamp article__timestamp flexbox__flex--1">美国东部时间 2023 年 7 月 23 日上午 10:27 </time></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display="NOT data.noSharing"><div class="share-bar"><amp-social-share type="system" width="72" height="24" data-param-url="https://www.wsj.com/articles/wokeness-hobbles-disney-as-it-faces-the-streaming-challenge-bob-iger-snow-white-7e1ac436"></amp-social-share></div></div><section subscriptions-section="content"><div class="media-object scope-
